Raise dead pet
Discworld ritual help
Raise dead pet


.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Raise dead pet -- Raises a player's pet from the dead.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This ritual raises pets from the dead.  You will need a holy
amulet, a holy symbol, and a prayer book with 'Walking the path'
inscribed as well as a block of incense to trade for the life of the pet.
.EP

